item.title: Changing home
item.dc:creator: @outrageouscape outrageouscape
item.description:
@outrageouscape wrote:

If it’s Delta it would be

Open up clickingMost.java. Search;

You’ll see this;

case 73100: case 4140: case 50235: c.triggerTele(X+misc.random(3), Y+misc.random(3), 0); break;

change the X and the Y to lumby

Or If that doesnt work Tele home and Type ::mypos and search for those coords in Client.java
